              </p>
              <p>
                <b id="comments-policy">OFFICIAL COMMENTS POLICY</b>
              </p>
              <p>Gundeals.me is a place for all members of the sportsman's community, both private and vendor, to post information on the best deals for related items on the internet. This privately owned forum reserves the right to limit the behavior of its members. The rules will be enforced in good faith to maintain discussion quality and peer respect.</p>
              <p>While Gundeals.me believes in free speech and limited censorship, certain rules will apply to the comment utility of this forum. These rules are intended to promote good will between the forum's members and vendors and encourage useful discussion about the gun deals posted on the site. gun.deals is a moderated website and retains the right to edit or delete any information posted that is in violation of the rules or is otherwise found to be counter to the intended purpose of the forum. The comment utility of this forum is intended for users to post useful information pertaining to the deal referenced in the post. Although all opinions are allowed, not all are useful. The best postings relate first hand information on the product referenced to the the post. Posting of first hand knowledge of a product or service is encouraged but not necessary.</p>
              <p>The following behaviors and/or activities are not permitted:</p>
              <p>1. Insulting, intimidating, bullying, harassing or other disrespectful or antisocial behavior.
                <br>2. Disruptive behavior of any sort, including Trolling and Threadjacking.
                <br>3. Rants or Raves
                <br>4. Offensive language. While mild language is tolerated it is discouraged. Vulgar and obscene language will not be tolerated and will be removed.
                <br>5. Posting or linking to pornography, illegal download sites, or illegal software.
                <br>6. Posting private correspondence on the forums without expressed permission of the author.
                <br>7. More than one account or multiple registrations.
                <br>8. Discussions promoting illegal activity .
                <br>9. Discussions of ethnicity, race, religion, or other divisive issues.
                <br>10. Posting in a language other than English without a translation.
                <br>11. Posts concerning moderator's directives or decisions, and reporting or reposting of such actions. Any mention of moderator decisions or activity will be immediately deleted and the poster may be banned.
                <br>12. Posts containing copyrighted material without permission of the copyright holder.
                <br>13. Posting your deals in multiple areas on the site. Deals should be posted in their appropriate area. Moderators have the right to move subject matter to it's appropriate area if necessary.
                <br>14. Using the private messaging system to make unsolicited commercial advances or violate the rules.
                <br>15. Posting another person's private information without their consent.
                <br>16. Posting irrelevant material or spamming.
                <br>17. Intentionally posting incorrect or flagrantly dangerous information or misquoting other's posts.
                <br>Single or repeated violations of these rules may subject a user to termination of their account. While warnings may be given, termination of a users account is at the discretion of the site management. (thanks, jmillerdoc).
                <br>18. Posting of deals with affiliate links are prohibited and may result in a ban.
              </p>
